9	 * Tests:
10	 *   T1: Pass-through mode (mti_enable=0) — data unchanged
11	 *   T2: First chirp muted (zeros) when MTI enabled
12	 *   T3: Second chirp = current - previous (correct subtraction)
13	 *   T4: Stationary target cancels to zero
14	 *   T5: Moving target (phase shift) passes through
15	 *   T6: Saturation on large difference
16	 *   T7: Enable toggle mid-stream — clean transition
17	 *   T8: Reset during operation — clean recovery
